            <title><![CDATA[【[并不简单]#冬季千万不要过度清洁皮肤#】#过度清洁皮肤当心皮肤屏障受损# 皮肤出现不能恢复的干燥、刺痛、红斑和脱皮等情况，都说明皮肤屏障已经受损了！[话筒...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#冬季千万不要过度清洁皮肤#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%B1%8F%E9%9A%9C%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E5%BA%A6%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%B1%8F%E9%9A%9C%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#过度清洁皮肤当心皮肤屏障受损#</span></a> 皮肤出现不能恢复的干燥、刺痛、红斑和脱皮等情况，都说明皮肤屏障已经受损了！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，一旦皮肤屏障功能受损，会导致皮肤水分流失，可能引发一些炎症性的皮肤疾病。⛄️冬季最常见的就是干燥性湿疹，主要发生在老年人和过度清洁皮肤的人群👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WHiB8T" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
