            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊]一串烤羊肉，深圳大叔染“怪病”！爱吃宵夜要注意】55岁的李大哥一如既往地站在烧烤摊前熟练地翻串、撒料，突然，他感到热浪阵阵袭来，翻串时双手的关节...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>一串烤羊肉，深圳大叔染“怪病”！爱吃宵夜要注意】55岁的李大哥一如既往地站在烧烤摊前熟练地翻串、撒料，突然，他感到热浪阵阵袭来，翻串时双手的关节和腰背部发酸发痛！随后几天，李大哥反复发高烧，双手关节和腰背部酸痛也越来越痛，上医院检查吃药后也还是反复发烧，于是赶紧前往深圳市人民医院。医生在询问李大哥病情时，偶然得知李大哥是卖羊肉烤串的，突然，医生眼前一亮：你的病可能跟你卖羊肉串有关系！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👉🏻 <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FSeY59Ar1iH5A0SyxQ_jmOw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">一串烤羊肉，深圳大叔染“怪病”！爱吃宵夜要注意</span></a> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjvmoo3zimg20av08ytjj.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
